properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued March 1 at 2:34PM EST until March 3 at 3:00AM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest winds 15 to 25 kt and seas 4 to 6 feet
expected.

* WHERE...Portions of Atlantic coastal waters.

* WHEN...From noon Monday to 3 AM EST Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM NOON MONDAY TO 3 AM EST TUESDAY
